@node Controls "GSEditor Control"
@next Controls
@prev Controls
@{JCENTER}
@{b}@{u}Controls@{uu}@{ub}

With @{b}GSEditor@{ub} you can change the Name, Unitname, ranking and the medals of the @{b}active@{ub} pilot.

You can control the editor by pressing a few buttons or selecting a menuitem.
When starting, there are only a few options available:
@{i}* New @{ui}
@{b}* Load @{ub}
@{i}@{b}* About @{ui}@{ub}
@{u}* Quit @{uu}
      
When starting the default path/filename is @{i}dh1:gs2000/roster.dat@{ui} and
the default save path/filename is @{u}@{b}RAM:dumroster.dat@{uu}@{ub}
but you can change this by editing the @{"ToolTypes" link ToolTypes}.
After loading all the options become available, including:

@{b}*Save
*Name
*Unitname
*Rank selecting
*Medal sliders@{ub}

@endnode

